{"tid":1174963,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"《7個王國與月影傭兵團》","createTime":"2019-05-28T08:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T08:54:30.000Z","uid":123430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b3af9f5d2792c68d4c3da91f80ceb35a13a4d9b9","tid":1174963,"uid":123430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:40:06.000Z","msg":"▍遊戲介紹<br />\n<br />\n本作是以 PVP 為主軸的對戰型模擬 RPG，講述受到魔王軍威脅的7個王國和心中有著各自想法的傭兵團，為了祖國的和平、家人或是財富名聲而投入戰場，展開一場激烈火熱的戰鬥。<br />\n<br />\n玩家需要合理分配行動值並活用角色制定戰術來取得勝利，遊戲最大的特色就是可與對手針對卡牌交易進行談判。此外，玩家也能在遊戲中體驗角色育成的樂趣。<br />\n<br />\n玩家可在主畫面上切換自己想使用的指揮官，每一位角色的指揮官技能也有所不同。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cVu63kT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcVu63kT.jpg&h=fcc55a43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n進入戰鬥後，隊伍中的角色將會化身為卡牌出現在場上，每一回合玩家都可抽一張技能卡，並安排場上的角色進行移動或攻擊，在限定的回合內將敵方擊敗即可獲勝。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ebnAcek.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FebnAcek.jpg&h=446f84c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩家可在陣型中查看自己所擁有的角色情報及技能卡，每個角色可移動和攻擊的範圍皆有不同，玩家可依照自己的策略編排最適合的陣容<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jBtLzsO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjBtLzsO.jpg&h=f563ce29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VdXcYUJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVdXcYUJ.jpg&h=72e52f6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cWj51jXvjK4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcWj51jXvjK4&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=05d5be6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cWj51jXvjK4</a><br />\n<br />\ngoogle play（日）<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mobcast.games.nkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.mobcast.games.nkg&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=297c9cad\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mobcast.games.nkg</a><br />\n<br />\nios (日)<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1394482030?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2Fid1394482030%3Fmt%3D8&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=88a8e4bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1394482030?mt=8</a><br />\n<br />\napk (qoo app)<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/7086\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.qoo-app.com%2Fapp%2F7086&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=723cd874\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/7086</a><br />\n<br />\nps:成個POST都係炒qoo app"},{"pid":"feb168907a9b598957dd5d8d001abeb16f8c1268","tid":1174963,"uid":19693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:46:48.000Z","msg":"出面有開post<br />\n<br />\n[I/A] 七個王國 月影の傭兵團 7つの王国と月影の傭兵団 - PVP 棋盤卡牌對戰 RPG！28/5 配信開始！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1174707\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1174707</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3dbf2343686784ca8a575b30bc5ee37174ae87d7","tid":1174963,"uid":103717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:54:30.000Z","msg":"我覺得隻game 無隔離post 講得咁差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n畫同特技都整得幾靚"}]}